FEATURE ENGINEERING & 전처리 =====================¶

A.지연율 등의 새 변수 생성¶

[ id + id ]

  1. ' id',' id' 1 .

    [ '' ]
    .
  2. orgdet_retio_delay : 'id+id' ( /)
  3. airline_retio_delay : '' ( /)
  4. month_retio_delay : '' ( /)
  5. week_retio_delay : '' ( /) : =>

    [ ]
  6. distance_orgdet : 'id+id'
  7. dist_rank : 'id+id'

B.변수 선택¶

: 7 + 6
(week,month,airline,distance,estimated_departure_time,estimated_arrival_time)
